HEADWORD: Inconsonant
<hw>In*con"so*nant</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <ety>[L.
<ets>inconsonans</ets>. See <er>In-</er> not, and
<er>Consonant</er>.]</ety> <def>Not consonant or agreeing; inconsistent;
discordant.</def> -- <wordforms><wf>In*con"so*nant*ly</wf>,
<pos>adv.</pos></wordforms>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

